<td>No ^c^ ^d^</td>
<td>No</td>
<td>No</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<p>^1^ Accepted as in possible and as in account won't get closed once notified about the account being anonymous. There is no statement about this type of payment being legal in any legislative.<br />
^2^ Or possible. Obviously not possible to use an internet based anonymizer for real world activities such as snail mail or meeting in person.</p>
