<p>^3^ Please note: Neither third parties are liable for money sent by mail. Do not send registered letters with reply advice.<br />
^4^ Payment by Western Union is possible only for 40 Euro and above. You have to pay the complete transaction fees and it may take up to a week until payment arrives.</p>
<p><font size="-3"><br />
Thanks to <a class="" href="https://anonymous-proxy-servers.net/" rel="nofollow">JonDos</a> (<a class="" href="https://anonymous-proxy-servers.net/forum/viewtopic.php?p=31220&amp;sid=ac8a6ca16eb768b3322be30b20375c97#p31220" rel="nofollow">Permission</a>). The "From Payment Receiver perspective" chapter of the Whonix Money wiki page contains content from the <a class="" href="https://shop.anonymous-proxy-servers.net/bin/payment?lang=en" rel="nofollow">JonDonym payment page</a>.<br />
</font></p>
<h1 id="from-payment-processor-perspective">From Payment Processor perspective</h1>
<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th>Method</th>
<th>Personal data</th>
<th>IP address</th>
<th>transaction history</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td>PayPal</td>
<td>Yes</td>
<td>Yes</td>
<td>Yes ^7^</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Western Union</td>
<td>?</td>
<td>Yes</td>
<td>Yes ^7^</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Anonymous credit card, Giftcard, Paysafecard, Ukash, etc.</td>
<td>^a^ ^b^</td>
<td>Yes</td>
<td>Yes ^7^</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Liberty Reserve</td>
<td>?</td>
<td>Yes</td>
<td>Yes ^7^</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Bitcoin</td>
<td>^6^</td>
<td>Yes</td>
<td>Yes ^8^</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Bank transfer</td>
<td>Yes</td>
<td>Yes</td>
